name: Dinari TQQQ
description: The Dinari TQQQ dShares token (TQQQ.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in the ProShares UltraPro QQQ ETF (TQQQ), a leveraged fund designed to provide three times the daily performance of the Nasdaq-100 Index. Each TQQQ.d token is fully backed by a corresponding TQQQ ETF share held securely in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, TQQQ.d offers investors efficient access to leveraged exposure to the Nasdaq-100, enabling 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
